// Local development code signing (Debug/Release).
//
// This COMMITTED file intentionally contains nothing sensitive. It optionally
// pulls in a git-ignored `Local.xcconfig`, where your personal
// DEVELOPMENT_TEAM lives — so a Team ID is never committed to this repo.
//
// If `Local.xcconfig` is absent (fresh clone, CI), the optional include below
// is silently skipped and the build behaves exactly as before (no team set).
//
// CI / TestFlight does NOT depend on this: the fastlane `beta` lane runs
// `update_code_signing_settings` after `xcodegen generate`, which overrides
// these values with manual signing + the `match` distribution profile. So the
// settings here only ever affect on-device development builds from Xcode.
#include? "Local.xcconfig"
